f         = \n| inhabloc_cat            = Town\n| inhabloc_cat_ref        = <ref name=\"StavropolK_admlist\" />\n| inhabloc_type           = \n| inhabloc_type_ref       = \n<!-- municipal status -->\n| mun_district_jur        = Budyonnovsky Municipal District\n| mun_district_jur_ref    = <ref name=\"StavropolK_mun1\" />\n| urban_okrug_jur         = \n| urban_okrug_jur_ref     = \n| urban_settlement_jur    = Budyonnovsk Urban Settlement\n| urban_settlement_jur_ref = <ref name=\"StavropolK_mun1\" />\n| rural_settlement_jur    = \n| rural_settlement_jur_ref = \n| inter_settlement_territory = \n| inter_settlement_territory_ref = \n| mun_admctr_of1          = Budyonnovsky Municipal District\n| mun_admctr_of1_ref      = <ref name=\"StavropolK_mun1\" />\n| mun_admctr_of2          = Budyonnovsk Urban Settlement\n| mun_admctr_of2_ref      = <ref name=\"StavropolK_mun1\" />\n| leader_title            = \n| leader_title_ref        = \n| leader_name             = \n| leader_name_ref         = \n| representative_body     = \n| representative_body_ref = \n<!-- statistics -->\n| elevation_m             = \n| area_km2                = 62.1\n| area_km2_ref            = <ref name=\"Area\">\u0423\u043f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u043b\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0440\u0435\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430 \u043f\u043e \u0421\u0442\u0430\u0432\u0440\u043e\u043f\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0441\u043a\u043e\u043c\u0443 \u043a\u0440\u0430\u044e. [http://to26.rosreestr.ru/upload/to26/files/doklad_2010_sk.pdf \u0414\u043e\u043a\u043b\u0430\u0434 \u043e \u0441\u043e\u0441\u0442\u043e\u044f\u043d\u0438\u0438 \u0438 \u0438\u0441\u043f\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0438 \u0437\u0435\u043c\u0435\u043b\u044c \u0421\u0442\u0430\u0432\u0440\u043e\u043f\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e \u043a\u0440\u0430\u044f \u0432 2010 \u0433\u043e\u0434\u0443]{{dead link|date=July 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, \u0441\u0442\u0440.&nbsp;54 {{in lang|ru}}</ref>\n| pop_2010census          = 64624\n| pop_2010census_rank     = 243rd\n| pop_2010census_ref      = <ref name=\"2010Census\">{{ru-pop-ref|2010Census}}</ref>\n| pop_latest              = \n| pop_latest_date         = \n| pop_latest_ref          = \n| population_demonym      = \n| time_zone_ref           = \n<!-- history -->\n| established_date        = 1799\n| established_title       = \n| established_date_ref    = <ref name=\"gr\" />\n| current_cat_date        = \n| current_cat_date_ref    = \n| abolished_date          = \n| abolished_date_ref      = \n<!-- misc -->\n| postal_codes            = 356800\u2013356803, 356805\u2013356809\n| postal_codes_ref        = \n| dialing_codes           = 86559\n| dialing_codes_ref       = \n| website                 = http://www.budennovsk-sk.ru/\n}}\n'''Budyonnovsk''' ({{lang-ru|\u0411\u0443\u0434\u0451\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0441\u043a}}), also spelled '''Budennovsk''', is a [[types of inhabited localities in Russia|town]] in [[Stavropol Krai]], [[Russia]]. Previously, it was named '''Svyatoy Krest''' ({{lang|ru|\u0421\u0432\u044f\u0442\u043e\u0301\u0439 \u041a\u0440\u0435\u0441\u0442}}, lit. \"holy cross\") and '''Prikumsk''' ({{lang|ru|\u041f\u0440\u0438\u043a\u0443\u0301\u043c\u0441\u043a}}).{{citation needed|date=February 2012}} Population: {{ru-census|p2010=64,624|p2002=65,687|p1989=55,350}}\n\n==History==\nIt was founded in 1799 by [[Armenians|Armenian]] settlers from [[Derbent]].<ref name=\"gr\">{{cite book|title=\u042d\u043d\u0446\u0438\u043a\u043b\u043e\u043f\u0435\u0434\u0438\u044f \u0413\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0434\u0430 \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u0438|year=2003|publisher=\u0411\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0448\u0430\u044f \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0430\u044f \u042d\u043d\u0446\u0438\u043a\u043b\u043e\u043f\u0435\u0434\u0438\u044f|location=Moscow|isbn=5-7107-7399-9|page=59}}</ref> During [[World War II]], Budyonnovsk was occupied by [[Wehrmacht|German troops]] from August&nbsp;18, 1942 to January&nbsp;10, 1943.\n\nThe [[Budyonnovsk hospital hostage crisis]] took place here on June 1995.\n\n==Administrative and municipal status==\nWithin the [[subdivisions of Russia#Administrative divisions|framework of administrative divisions]], Budyonnovsk serves as the [[administrative center]] of [[Budyonnovsky District]], even though it is not a part of it.<ref name=\"StavropolK_admlist\">Resolution #63-p</ref> As an administrative division, it is incorporated separately as the '''[[city of federal subject significance|town of krai significance]] of Budyonnovsk'''\u2014an administrative unit with the status equal to that of the [[administrative divisions of Stavropol Krai|districts]].<ref name=\"StavropolK_admlist\" /> As a [[subdivisions of Russia#Municipal divisions|municipal division]], the town of krai significance of Budyonnovsk is incorporated within Budyonnovsky Municipal District as '''Budyonnovsk Urban Settlement'''.<ref name=\"StavropolK_mun1\">Law #88-kz</ref>\n\n==Climate==\n\n==Military==\nAn airbase is located 14 km (9 miles) northwest of the town.\n\n==Religion==\nOn July&nbsp;1, 2010, an [[Armenian Apostolic Church|Armenian apostolic church]] was opened in Budyonnovsk.<ref name=\"Church\">News.am. [http://news.am/eng/news/23890.html Armenian church opened in Budenovsk]</ref>\n\n==References==\n[[File:\u0412\u043e\u043a\u0437\u0430\u043b \u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0446\u0438\u0438 \u0411\u0443\u0434\u0451\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0441\u043a.JPG|thumb|[[Budyonovsk railway station]]]]\n\n===Notes===\n{{Reflist}}\n\n===Sources===\n*{{RussiaAdmMunRef|sta|adm|list}}\n*{{RussiaAdmMunRef|sta|mun|list1}}\n\n{{Stavropol Krai}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=October 2012}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Stavropol Krai]]\n[[Category:Stavropol Governorate]]\n[[Category:Populated places established in 1799]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Russian inhabited locality\n| en_name                 = Budyonnovsk\n| ru_name                 = \u0411\u0443\u0434\u0451\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0441\u043a\n| loc_name1               = \n| loc_lang1               = \n| loc_name2               = \n| loc_lang2               = \n| loc_name3               = \n| loc_lang3               = \n| loc_name4               = \n| loc_lang4               = \n| other_name              = \n| other_lang              = \n| image_skyline           = Buden monument.jpg\n| image_caption           = [[Mother Motherland]] statue in the town\n| image_map               = \n| map_caption             = \n| coordinates             = {{coord|44|47|N|44|10|E|display=inline,title}}\n| image_flag              = Flag of Budyonnovsk.svg\n| flag_caption            = \n| image_coa               = Coat of Arms of Budyonnovsk (Stavropol krai).png\n| coa_caption             = \n| anthem                  = \n| anthem_ref              = \n| holiday                 = \n| holiday_ref             = \n<!-- administrative status -->\n| federal_subject         = [[Stavropol Krai]]\n| federal_subject_ref     = <ref name=\"StavropolK_admlist\" />\n| adm_district_jur        = \n| adm_district_jur_ref    = \n| adm_inhabloc_jur        = [[city of federal subject significance|town of krai significance]] of Budyonnovsk\n| adm_inhabloc_jur_ref    = <ref name=\"StavropolK_admlist\" />\n| adm_citydistrict_jur    = \n| adm_citydistrict_type   = \n| adm_citydistrict_jur_ref = \n| adm_selsoviet_jur       = \n| adm_selsoviet_type      = \n| adm_selsoviet_jur_ref   = \n| capital_of              = \n| capital_of_ref          = \n| adm_ctr_of1             = town of krai significance of Budyonnovsk\n| adm_ctr_of1_ref         = <ref name=\"StavropolK_admlist\" />\n| adm_ctr_of2             = [[Budyonnovsky District]]\n| adm_ctr_of2_ref         = <ref name=\"StavropolK_admlist\" />\n| adm_ctr_of3             = \n| adm_ctr_of3_ref         = \n| inhabloc_cat            = Town\n| inhabloc_cat_ref        = <ref name=\"StavropolK_admlist\" />\n| inhabloc_type           = \n| inhabloc_type_ref       = \n<!-- municipal status 